{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we used the A549 (ATCC number: CCL-185) cell line isolated from a patient with lung cancer.",
    "We prepared the FFPE block and FF sample from the same batch of the cultured A549 cells.",
    "DNAs extracted from matched samples were subjected to WES and targeted capture sequencing with a custom cancer panel.",
    "After WES, we observed that the insert fragments from the FFPE block (median length: 147 bp) were shorter than those from the matched FF (median length: 221 bp) (Supplementary Fig.",
    "S2) similar to data from clinical samples (Fig. 1B-F)."
  ]
}